            </svg>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
    
  </div>

  <hr class="border-t-1 border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.051)]">
  <!-- Testimonial Section -->
  <div class="mt-5 mb-5 sm:w-5/6 text-base mx-auto pl-4 sm:pl-0">
    <h2 class="text-4xl mb-5">Agency members stand out from the crowd</h2>
      <p class="mb-5 text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">A small selection of our members and what they're saying about The Agency</p>
    <div class="px-4 w-full mx-auto">      
      <div class="mx-auto w-5/6">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 justify-center mx-auto ">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/simmon",
                alt:"Description of Image",
                class:"w-full rounded object-cover justify-center"
                %>
            </div>

            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-5">Simmon</h3>
              <p class="italic text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">
                "The Agency of Learning provided me with the next building block in my transition into a career in software development. It had the structure I was looking for to boost my 
                confidence about my next step. With guidance on open source issues I could participate in, access to seniors and folks already in the industry to help get unstuck, 
                The Agency supercharged my network."
              </p> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 justify-center mx-auto ">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/nathan",
                alt:"Description of Image",
                class:"w-full rounded object-cover justify-center"
                %>
            </div>

            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-5">Nathan</h3>
              <p class="italic text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">
                "Man, I kind of feel like I struck gold when I applied to this program."
              </p> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 justify-center mx-auto ">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/cody",
                alt:"Description of Image",
                class:"w-full rounded object-cover justify-center"
                %>
            </div>

            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-5">Cody</h3>
              <p class="italic text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">
                "A strong culture of mentorship is vital for ensuring the future of our community. 
                I’ve been fortunate enough to work with Ruby professionally for almost a decade now and want to make sure that’s 
                a future available to others."
              </p> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 justify-center mx-auto ">
              <%= image_tag "welcome/alex",
                alt:"Description of Image",
                class:"w-full rounded object-cover justify-center"
                %>
            </div>

            <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-3xl mb-5">Alex</h3>
              <p class="italic text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">
                "I'm 100% convinced that this is how we cultivate the next generation of truly powerful software engineers."
              </p> 
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="border-t-1 border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.051)]">
  <!-- "The Pain" -->
  <div class="py-12 mb-5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 text-center font-extrabold ">Being a junior dev is lonely</h2>

      <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  mx-auto grid justify-items-end ">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/the_pain.jpeg", class:" rounded object-cover ", alt:"Description of Image" %>
          </div>
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
            <p class="text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">
              <span class="p">"Joining a developer community helps you meet peers, get advice, get unstuck, practice tricky situations, and grow your network.</span> <br>
              <span class="p">Mentorship and collaboration are also very hard to find when you’re solo.</span> <br>
              <span class="p">That’s what The Agency of Learning is for."</span> <br>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="border-t-1 border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.051)]">
  <!--  Members Benefits -->
  <div class="py-12 mb-5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl mb-8 text-center font-extrabold ">Member Benefits</h2>

      <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  mx-auto grid justify-items-end ">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/real_code.jpeg", class:" rounded object-cover ", alt:"Description of Image" %>
          </div>

          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
            <strong>Real code, real peers</strong>
            <p class="text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">Work together on software projects on a team with other developers. Get feedback on your code from experienced engineers. Talk to users.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
            <strong>Mastermind Community</strong>
            <p class="text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">Gain access to our private Discord community to connect with other members, attend daily standups, ask questions, get unstuck, and grow your skills.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  mx-auto grid justify-items-end ">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/master_mind.jpeg", class:" rounded object-cover ", alt:"Description of Image" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  mx-auto grid justify-items-end ">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/career_services.jpeg", class:" rounded object-cover ", alt:"Description of Image" %>
          </div>

          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2 max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
            <strong>Career Services</strong>
            <p class="text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]" >Get job ready with resume review and coding exercises. Wow your first employer by learning how to give great verbal and written status updates.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex justify-center mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-1 flex-col md:flex-row">
          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  max-w-prose mx-auto flex-1">
            <strong>Hiring Partner Network</strong>
            <p class="text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.678)]">We'll feature you in our periodic outreach to our hiring partners - a small, motivated network of companies looking to hire early career talent.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-2 w-full md:w-1/2  mx-auto grid justify-items-end ">
            <%= image_tag "welcome/hiring_networks.jpeg", class:" rounded object-cover ", alt:"Description of Image" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
 
  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="text-white flex justify-left items-center p-5">
    <div class="w-1/2 pl-8">
      <button class="flex justify-between items-center w-full h-[60px] mb-2 bg-[#38D68E] text-[#363942] font-bold px-4 rounded-lg hover:scale-105 transform transition-transform">
          Become a Member
